  "summary": "Malicious code in @sqlite-list/createsql (npm)",
  "details": "The package index.js fetches a remote script from a GitHub gist (getchainverse/198a0bbec7a6018e9250615d26e37b90 or getchainverse/b57a92378ad0a52430137c3b810e7107) via the GitHub API and executes it with eval(). The gist content is attacker-controlled and can be changed at any time, making this a remote-code-execution dropper. The package has no repository, no description, and no lifecycle hooks — the payload runs when the module is required.",
